435
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] zašto da se ljudi boje?

436
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto onda ne idu u crkveni brak?

437
00:34:50,519 --> 00:34:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ili, zašto jednostavno govore

438
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] neke loše stvari o braku?

439
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže dalje, crkveni brak nije samo lijepi obred,

440
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego je sakramenat.

441
00:35:01,239 --> 00:35:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Krist ulazi u vašu odnos.

442
00:35:03,599 --> 00:35:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] I to smo isto lijepo čuli danas

443
00:35:05,119 --> 00:35:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] od fra Stjepana.

444
00:35:06,639 --> 00:35:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, dvije osobe sklapaju brak,

445
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] a uvijek su tri osobe prisutne.

446
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zaručnik, zaručnika,

447
00:35:13,579 --> 00:35:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] zaručnica i sam gospodin.

448
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje,

449
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] daje nam milost da se volite

450
00:35:20,639 --> 00:35:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao što Bog voli.

451
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerno, žrtveno i do kraja.

452
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vaš brak postaje znak Bože ljubavi svijetu.

453
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] I katekizam kaže,

454
00:35:28,599 --> 00:35:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] izvaljano sklopljena i dovršene ženitbe

455
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] nastaje trajna i isključiva veza

456
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] između supružnika.

457
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] To nije zatvor,

458
00:35:38,019 --> 00:35:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] to je prostor slobode i sigurnosti.

459
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Za one koji su u civilnom braku,

460
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] crkva vas ne prezire.

461
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, postoji oni koji su u civilnom braku,

462
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] niste prezreni,

463
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali ipak puninu,

464
00:35:50,519 --> 00:35:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] ako možete sklopiti sveti crkveni brak,

465
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] a ne samo civilni,

466
00:35:54,380 --> 00:35:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda ulazite u sakramenat.

467
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi parovi svjedoče

468
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] kako se njihov odnos produbio

469
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] kada su primili crkveni brak.

470
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] Za mlade koji se spremaju za brak.

471
00:36:04,139 --> 00:36:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je sad, ono,

472
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj tražiti samo kemiju ili romantiku,

473
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] da, i blizu sam krajom.

474
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] I nemoj se sa tom osobom

475
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] sa kojom se,

476
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] malo još,

477
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] brzinski ću,

478
00:36:18,539 --> 00:36:19,800
[SPEAKER_00] primijetio sam ga.

479
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] A dobro.

480
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, skratit ću malo.

481
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, nemoj se uspoređivati sa drugima,

482
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] nego gradi autetičnu ljubav.

483
00:36:32,239 --> 00:36:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, svi smo danas bombardirani

484
00:36:34,199 --> 00:36:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] sa koje kakvim tim Facebookom

485
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] i tim ostalim stvarima.

486
00:36:38,079 --> 00:36:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] A šta je istina?

487
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Istina je stvaran život.

488
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovo je sve nešto uljepšavanje.

489
00:36:43,019 --> 00:36:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nemojte nasist na to.

490
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Onda psalam nam kaže,

491
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] divna su dijela tvoja,

492
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] dušu moju,

493
00:36:49,559 --> 00:36:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] do dna si poznavao.

494
00:36:51,039 --> 00:36:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, odkupljeni smo

495
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovom krvlju.

496
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] Autentična ljubav,

497
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] koja ide prema braku,

498
00:36:57,719 --> 00:36:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] otvorena je životu.

499
00:37:00,380 --> 00:37:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

500
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] sad sam na kraju.

501
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako,

502
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] znaš ono misao,

503
00:37:06,719 --> 00:37:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] mladi danas ne mogu živjeti čisto,

504
00:37:08,940 --> 00:37:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, to je nemoguće.

505
00:37:10,139 --> 00:37:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] A to je kao kad kažeš,

506
00:37:11,659 --> 00:37:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] nemoguće voziti po ograničenju auto,

507
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno je sam sebi dao gaz.

508
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nije čovječe.

509
00:37:18,099 --> 00:37:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kako?

510
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] Neko je stisko taj gaz.

511
00:37:20,659 --> 00:37:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] E, tako je ovo.

512
00:37:21,659 --> 00:37:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, živi čestito,

513
00:37:23,099 --> 00:37:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] živi čisto.

514
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovisi o tebi.

515
00:37:25,539 --> 00:37:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ovisi o svakome od nas.

516
00:37:27,340 --> 00:37:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] I, evo, još jedna stvar,

517
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] misao iz Bože riječi.

518
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bog kaže,

519
00:37:33,079 --> 00:37:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sve činim novo.

520
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] Budite nova stvorenja,

521
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] rođeni,

522
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] očišćeni,

523
00:37:39,199 --> 00:37:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] oslobođeni

524
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] i odkupljeni za Krista,

525
00:37:41,739 --> 00:37:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] za njegovu zarožnicu,

526
00:37:43,260 --> 00:37:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] za svetu crkvu

527
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] i u konačnici

528
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] budite otvoreni

529
00:37:47,679 --> 00:37:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] za vječnost.

530
00:37:48,679 --> 00:37:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] A to je to.

531
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin nas želi nagraditi,

532
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] a na namo je

533
00:37:52,699 --> 00:37:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] da dođemo u vječnost.

534
00:37:54,239 --> 00:37:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, hvala vam na pažnji.

535
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala Isus i Marija.

536
00:37:57,000 --> 00:38:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bol vas blagoslovio.

